Diagram 3 (Only Small)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's cut at 01 gives up the chance of a big profit in exchange for something small...
\par
\par Black does not connect but instead plays dansu at 2 and sacrifices the four black stones.
\par
\par Now, black can live with 4.
\par
\par White has failed to capture the whole black group.
\par }
